    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You're not rendering the RefinementList if there's no results, so the refinement gets cleared. You can avoid this by:\n\n1. add `future.preserveSharedStateOnUnmount true` (https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/instantsearch/react/#widget-param-preservesharedstateonunmount)\n2. render the widgets that have a refinement (possibly virtual, only the hook) without conditional",
